{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"15d190c2aa","title":"“人事制度不合理”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9706c5e82d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"15d190c2aa"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"089db5dff9","name":"马槐亭"},{"id":"291d764b2e","name":"李永涛"},{"id":"4813fdc0bb","name":"马万钧"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"a031d2aeb3","name":"李伯祯"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7d0053008a","type":"title","text":"“人事制度不合理”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"fb19bbd8c4","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院马槐亭李永涛马万钧李伯祯","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"a3a3dabfd3","type":"paragraph","text":"“人事科神秘莫测，是阎罗殿，是宗派主义堡垒”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"d139004844","type":"paragraph","text":"马槐亭说：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"e6d7db589d","type":"paragraph","text":"“人事制度不合理，保密制度扩大化。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"d88464c3e0","type":"paragraph","text":"李永涛说：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"099f4f0e1b","type":"paragraph","text":"“人事科是阎罗殿，档案是生死簿，大笔一勾决定一生的命运”，“过去自己在中学表现不好，现在不知档案里给我写了些什么”，“原想报考航空学院而没有取上，恐怕就是这个原因，因此极力赞成公布人事档案”，“资本家都能掌握自己的命运，难道我们不能吗？”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"2c743ab666","type":"paragraph","text":"马万钧说：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"3255ddb144","type":"paragraph","text":"“现在人事处下面有一科，二科，三科，分得太多，人事处实是起了公安部门的特派作用，不仅不解决问题，还和你找麻烦……同时机构太多不起作用……选择人材时只从政治好出发……学校副院长太多，应降一级”。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"4e510cda46","type":"paragraph","text":"李伯祯说：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"a37920f6b3","type":"paragraph","text":"“分配生产实习是唯成份论，资料员管的严”，认为把他当成特务。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"f2dc5288de","type":"paragraph","text":"“人事科坏现象多，是个死角。不要以为只有部分人（党、团员）爱国，群众也是爱国的。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"},{"id":"889d21672b","type":"paragraph","text":"“政治工作人员只拿钱不干活”，宿舍中派了团员来，他认为是来监视他的。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa"}],"page":{"id":"7df47e89c8","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"15d190c2aa","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}